    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a heavy way to put it. but i feel like you're right... it's not even just that the work is bad, it's that the person who made it feels empty. like there's no point in just sitting around in this shell once the soul of it has left. what's even the purpose of staying when the thing that made you *you* is gone?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
